ee, Vernon}}\n[[Category:1900 births]]\n[[Category:1992 deaths]]\n[[Category:American Marine Corps personnel of World War II]]\n[[Category:Burials at Arlington National Cemetery]]\n[[Category:Oklahoma State University alumni]]\n[[Category:People of the Banana Wars]]\n[[Category:People from Tulsa, Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Legion of Merit]]\n[[Category:United States Marine Corps generals]]\n[[Category:University of Texas at Austin alumni]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Distinguished Service Medal (US Army)]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Navy and Marine Corps Medal]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Military Merit (Korea)]]\n[[Category:Battle of Iwo Jima]]\n[[Category:Air Corps Tactical School alumni]]\n", "name_user": "WFinch", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eIn retirement", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vernon_E._Megee"}
